  56,32,"وَفَاكِهَةٍ كَثِيرَ‌ةٍ (and a lot of fruits...56:32). The word Kathirah [ abounding ] has two senses: [ 1] there will be plenty of fruits; and [ 2] there will be an uncountable variety and kinds of fruits."
